item.title: CVE-2017-2252|2024-08-05T13:48:04.478Z -- sourcenext%20corporation -- self-extracting%20archive%20files%20created%20by%20file%20compact
item.description: Untrusted search path vulnerability in self-extracting archive files created by File Compact Ver.5 version 5.10 and earlier, Ver.6 version 6.02 and earlier, Ver.7 version 7.02 and earlier allows an attacker to gain privileges via a Trojan horse DLL in an unspecified directory.
